title: Srah Reang
text: Srah Reang is a "<a href="khum">khum</a>" (<a href="Administrative%20divisions%20of%20Cambodia">commune</a>) of <a href="Mongkol%20Borei%20District">Mongkol Borei District</a> in <a href="Banteay%20Meanchey%20Province">Banteay Meanchey Province</a> in western <a href="Cambodia">Cambodia</a>.
